N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 7200.7 - Fees for copies of records

State Regulations

The fee for copies of records shall be 25 cents per page
not in excess of 9 inches by 14 inches, or the actual cost of reproducing any
other record. Notes
